<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>New Device Login</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;
      max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; } .warning {
      background-color: #FEF3C7; border: 1px solid #F59E0B; padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; } .details { background-color:
      #F3F4F6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>New Device Login Detected</h2>

    <div class='warning'>
      <p>A new device was used to access your SyncBridge account.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='details'>
      <h3>Device Details:</h3>
      <p>Device: {{deviceName}}</p>
      <p>Location: {{location}}</p>
      <p>Time: {{timestamp}}</p>
      <p>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>If this was you, you can ignore this email. If you don't recognize this
      activity, please:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Change your password immediately</li>
      <li>Review your account activity</li>
      <li>Contact support if you need assistance</li>
    </ol>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The SyncBridge Security Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>